<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hóa Đơn Thu Hoạch</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2c3e50;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .invoice-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .invoice-info .section {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .invoice-info h3 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .invoice-info p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .invoice-info .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        table thead {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
        }
        
        table th {
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        table td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        table tbody tr:hover {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .text-right {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .totals {
            margin-left: auto;
            width: 350px;
            border-top: 2px solid #2c3e50;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .totals .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .totals .row.total {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #27ae60;
            border-top: 2px solid #2c3e50;
            padding-top: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .totals .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .number {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>HÓA ĐƠN THU HOẠCH</h1>
        <p>Harvest Invoice</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="invoice-info">
        <div class="section">
            <h3>Thông Tin Hóa Đơn</h3>
            <p><span class="label">Số hóa đơn:</span> {{ticketNumber}}</p>
            <p><span class="label">Ngày:</span> {{date}}</p>
            <p><span class="label">Phương thức thanh toán:</span> {{paymentMethod}}</p>
            {{#if accountNumber}}
            <p><span class="label">Số tài khoản:</span> {{accountNumber}}</p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h3>Thông Tin Lịch Thu Hoạch</h3>
            {{#if harvestScheduleId}}
            <p><span class="label">Mã lịch:</span> {{harvestScheduleId.id}}</p>
            {{#if harvestScheduleId.description}}
            <p><span class="label">Mô tả:</span> {{harvestScheduleId.description}}</p>
            {{/if}}
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: #2c3e50;">Chi Tiết Thu Hoạch</h3>
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th class="text-center">STT</th>
                <th>Sản phẩm</th>
                <th class="text-center">Đơn vị</th>
                <th class="text-right">Số lượng</th>
                <th class="text-right">Đơn giá</th>
                <th class="text-right">Thuế (%)</th>
                <th class="text-right">Thành tiền</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each details}}
            <tr>
                <td class="text-center">{{add @index 1}}</td>
                <td>{{product.name}}</td>
                <td class="text-center">{{unit}}</td>
                <td class="text-right number">{{formatNumber quantity}}</td>
                <td class="text-right number">{{formatCurrency unitPrice}}</td>
                <td class="text-right number">{{formatNumber taxRate}}</td>
                <td class="text-right number">{{formatCurrency amount}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>
    
    <div class="totals">
        <div class="row">
            <span class="label">Tổng số lượng:</span>
            <span class="number">{{formatNumber quantity}} {{unit}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <span class="label">Tổng tiền hàng:</span>
            <span class="number">{{formatCurrency totalAmount}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <span class="label">VAT:</span>
            <span class="number">{{formatCurrency vatAmount}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row total">
            <span>TỔNG THANH TOÁN:</span>
            <span class="number">{{formatCurrency totalPayment}}</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Cảm ơn quý khách đã sử dụng dịch vụ của chúng tôi!</p>
        <p>Mọi thắc mắc xin vui lòng liên hệ bộ phận chăm sóc khách hàng</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
